{"tid":1219672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求民陣轉宣傳口號","createTime":"2019-06-14T00:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T00:48:26.000Z","uid":260460,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92e528157fc1842f6bf5929651c877df82ffed55","tid":1219672,"uid":260460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:23:42.000Z","msg":"其實上次出黎既人係知道發生緊咩事 <br />\n要令佢地再出黎<br />\n我建議用<strong>感性</strong>既口號 <br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你甘心嗎 </span></strong><br />\n你甘心就咁完結嗎<br />\n你還未放棄嗎 <br />\n你團火還在嗎<br />\n你甘願放棄嗎 <br />\n等等<br />\n<br />\n類似既口號 <br />\n簡而有力 <br />\n令人回想初衷<br />\n<br />\n總好過又用 抗送中 反惡法 <br />\n呢類大家都聽左好多次幾口號<br />\n<br />\n求集思廣益同正評"},{"pid":"06ec569ddf9ce958397c73008a523edcc760095a","tid":1219672,"uid":260460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:30:26.000Z","msg":"你甘心就咁完？"},{"pid":"95b349b2b0926074a200fa682be5fddcc2b7e729","tid":1219672,"uid":156509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:30:53.000Z","msg":"送你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10179207327cfe769ded75e08e01d18a9d681aa","tid":1219672,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"平反612<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b553eab09c0ece9b7e87c9df678858e35eb969e4","tid":1219672,"uid":260460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:32:54.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"bc3429adebbc9eb75b9369737a38f037e92508ce","tid":1219672,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d10179207327cfe769ded75e08e01d18a9d681aa","tid":1219672,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"平反612<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:35:06.000Z","msg":"追究血腥鎮壓責任"},{"pid":"88cad74afd6a9d3bdb2410d762fe2efcdbdea358"